    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-808e-bec0-e6a6a6bd276c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors propose an online educational design for collaborative learning in Problem-Based Learning using Group Contracts and Peer-Evaluation. Both conscructs were found to be helpful in helping group members achieve their goals, providing useful insights for online learning UX design.",
